  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073960/extras/ceaba447406c561f82c1eaa90fb20fda.avif?t=1662381466\" width=400 height=200 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Find Nurie, the cat that disappeared while I was getting the feed!</h2><br>The protagonist and the cat (Nuri) who lived in a peaceful countryside<br>While you're on your way to get food, you suddenly go to the mountains to find a cat who left the house<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073960/extras/483ca4a20b160316b3f86e8c33468fba.apng?t=1662381466\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073960/extras/483ca4a20b160316b3f86e8c33468fba.poster.avif?t=1662381466\" class=\"bb_img\" width=64 height=64 /></picture></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073960/extras/76659d4a7e4c3527970daff7185cf1db.apng?t=1662381466\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073960/extras/76659d4a7e4c3527970daff7185cf1db.poster.avif?t=1662381466\" class=\"bb_img\" width=64 height=64 /></picture></span><br>- The main character who goes to find the cat who left the house<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2073960/extras/b7f632c413eb458cd146a460e0e4d8bf.avif?t=1662381466\" width=68 height=75 /></span><br>- Noori, the cat that left the house<br><br><strong>an incessant movement </strong><br><strong>You can't stop once you move the main character unless it's under certain conditions</strong> The <strong>movement (←,→) given to the protagonist is only jump (C) and change direction </strong><br>It's going to be a harder game because it can't be stopped<br><br><strong>a spirit of challenge</strong><br>When you make a bad jump, you come up to find the cat on the top, but if you fall down the endless mountain, you'll feel pain<br>Once you're used to it and you're aware of the game's movement, the jump system, you'll be able to clear it without difficulty<br><br><strong>Please go up to the top of the mountain and find Nuri!</strong>",
